<title>FRANCE: EU to decide Thomson sale, recapitalisation on Dec 4.</title>
<headline>EU to decide Thomson sale, recapitalisation on Dec 4.</headline>
<dateline>PARIS 1996-11-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>The European Commission is expected to make statements on competition aspects of the privatisation of the Thomson SA electronics group on December 4, and its recapitalisation on December 18, a French newspaper reported on Thursday.</p>
<p>La Tribune, citing a news agency report, said the Commission would give its view on the proposed acquisition of Thomson-CSF by Lagardere Groupe and the Multimedia unit by Daewoo Electronics on December 4.</p>
<p>It will rule on the state's 11 billion franc capital injection into Thomson on December 18, it said.</p>
<p>Lagardere's proposed acquisition of Thomson and Daewoo's control of Thomson Multimedia were notified to the Commission for clearance under the merger regulation on October 31.</p>
